.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, trike, car
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person driving the car is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Transport           | roller | snowmobile | trike     | car |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

