.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, woodworking, collecting, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | collecting   | woodworking         | writing   | hiking    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

