.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, car, airplane, train
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person driving the car##7
2. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the trike##7
4. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | car   | airplane | train | trike    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

