.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, biathlon, baseball, cycling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
6. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the person who's sport is cycling is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Sport          | cycling | ice-hockey | biathlon  | baseball |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

