.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, dutch, colombian
1. the argentine is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the colombian is somewhere between the person drinking water and the dutch##7
3. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
4. the colombian is not to the left of the canadian##8
5. the colombian is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the canadian is on the left of the dutch##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Nationality      | canadian | dutch | colombian  | argentine |

