.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-11::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, guinea-pig, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
3. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
5. the person driving the car is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Pet   | chinchilla     | goldfish | guinea-pig | turtle |
| Transport     | quad-bike | scooter  | car    | boat   |

