.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, onion, pineapple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, swisher, aristoff, havana
1. the person eating onion is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
2. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the havana-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime        | pineapple | onion      | corn    |
| Cigar   | bolivar | aristoff   | swisher | havana |

