.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff, tiparillo, oliveros
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the davidoff-smoker##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | oliveros | davidoff         | tiparillo    | old-henry       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

