4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the hamster##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk | tea        | sprite       |
| Pet      | hamster | cat  | hedgehog | guinea-pig |

