.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, social-worker, librarian, freelancer
 1. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the librarian##1
 4. the librarian is not to the right of the social-worker##8
 5. the freelancer is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the social-worker is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the librarian##8
 9. the social-worker is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the project-manager##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Job   | project-manager | freelancer  | librarian     | social-worker    |

