.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, rabbit, snake
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, pink, light-blue, lavender
1. the owner of the snake is not the person who likes light-blue##6
2. the person who likes light-blue is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lavender##5
6. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the right of the person who likes pink##8
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who likes lavender##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | cat  | snake | fish  | rabbit  |
| Color   | aquamarine | pink   | lavender | light-blue |

