.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
City: paris, new-york, san-francisco, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to new-york is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person traveling to paris##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to paris##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| City   | new-york | edinburgh      | san-francisco     | paris     |

 